From the ASUC Facebook page (https://www.facebook.com/theASUC/) : "IClicker rentals will be occurring in 540 Eshleman Hall Wednesday-Friday 1/22-1/24 from 11 am to 1 pm. The rental charge is $5 and CalID is required to check out an iClicker. At this time we are only able to do transactions via credit or debit card and do not take cash or Venmo."

--

The ASUC does $5 rentals, though I haven't seen advertisements for it this semester yet I would check if they're doing it again this semester.

Also the cal student store has iclickers for rent for 17$ I think?
